3. the indonesian is in the middle##1
4. the indonesian is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is badminton##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
